      </modifiers>
      <rules>
        <rule name="Funerary Rites" id="93df-d386-5119-49ac" hidden="false">
          <description>Priests of Morr are not wizards by any means, however, they do have numerous Funerary Rites, which they may perform.


As such, priests of Morr may choose a Funerary Rite listed below, using the rules for Magic on page 56 of the Mordheim hook.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="Loner" id="bb74-5d7d-c94b-85ff" hidden="false">
          <description>Few people care to spend any length of time in the company of a priest of Morr - even when it is their duty to do so.


As such, a priest of Morr is used to being alone and probably prefers it that way. 


Priests of Morr do not suffer from the All Alone rules.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
    </selectionEntry>
